General.Name: Gold-Zack AG
General.Description: Gold-Zack AG is a European investment group for small- and medium-sized companies in growth markets. Gold-Zack was formerly an Internet service provider, but the company has changed its focus towards the investment market. Services provided by the Gold-Zack group cover the value creation chain for the growing enterprise. The company also deals with start-up financing and consulting; all the way to the initial public offering and comprehensive services for publicly traded companies. In these areas Gold-Zack focuses especially on the sectors of the future: e-Business, Telecommunications, Media, Sport, Entertainment and Life Sciences/Biotechnology. The company is based in Mettmann, Germany. As of October 1, 2003 Gold-Zack AG is in liquidation.
